Name: Freed Soft
About the game: Freed Soft - is a simulator in which you have to create your own IT company. In this world, you will have to compete with other IT companies for a place in the market in the software industry. Create your own companies, become an IT leader. You will have to: Start your own IT company. Collect a variety of items. Create and improve software. Build and develop your own office.
